{"parentUuid":"8785d2fa-8416-4ea1-94a4-dd10d83701fe","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"93a6a750-cac6-4089-83af-db89b813ea32","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014NS2X522gPJUMjoWG9xr5b","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→CREATE FUNCTION update_updated_at()\n     2→RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\n     3→BEGIN\n     4→  NEW._updated_at = NOW();\n     5→  RETURN NEW;\n     6→END;\n     7→$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n     8→\n     9→\n    10→CREATE EXTENSION ltree;\n    11→\n    12→CREATE TABLE \"categories\" (\n    13→    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    14→    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    15→    path ltree NOT NULL,\n    16→\n    17→    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    18→    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n    19→);\n    20→\n    21→CREATE TABLE \"courses\" (\n    22→    course_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    23→    title TEXT NOT NULL,\n    24→    description TEXT NOT NULL,\n    25→    slug TEXT NOT NULL,\n    26→    tags JSONB NOT NULL,\n    27→    publish_status TEXT NOT NULL,\n    28→    category_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES categories(category_id),\n    29→    published_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    30→    last_updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    31→\n    32→    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    33→    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n    34→);\n    35→\n    36→CREATE TRIGGER trigger_courses_updated_at\n    37→    BEFORE UPDATE ON courses\n    38→    FOR EACH ROW\n    39→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at();\n    40→\n    41→COMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n    42→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"uuid":"9170afdb-e9ad-419d-91f8-bfbeecb718f9","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:00:43.671Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku/apps/api/migrations/000001_add_courses.up.sql","content":"CREATE FUNCTION update_updated_at()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n  NEW._updated_at = NOW();\n  RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\n\nCREATE EXTENSION ltree;\n\nCREATE TABLE \"categories\" (\n    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    path ltree NOT NULL,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE \"courses\" (\n    course_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    title TEXT NOT NULL,\n    description TEXT NOT NULL,\n    slug TEXT NOT NULL,\n    tags JSONB NOT NULL,\n    publish_status TEXT NOT NULL,\n    category_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES categories(category_id),\n    published_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    last_updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_courses_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON courses\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at();\n\nCOMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n","numLines":42,"startLine":1,"totalLines":42}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"8785d2fa-8416-4ea1-94a4-dd10d83701fe","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"d6c1023f-0aa7-4494-96ba-45f65a369f36","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"enumerated-spinning-grove"}
{"parentUuid":"9170afdb-e9ad-419d-91f8-bfbeecb718f9","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01FUH2gXqxTUZbUKddW5dva8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"CLAUDE.md のルールと照らし合わせてレビューします。\n\n---\n\n**問題点**\n\n1. **`categories` テーブルに `_updated_at` トリガーがない**\n   - `courses` にはトリガーが設定されているが、`categories` には未設定。ルールで「update 時に `update_updated_at()` を呼び出すトリガーを設定する」とある。\n\n2. **`courses.description` が `NOT NULL`**\n   - 説明文が必須かどうかはアプリ要件次第だが、新規作成時に空でも登録できるようにする場合は `NULL` 許容が妥当。（要件確認）\n\n3. **`courses.last_updated_at` の意味が `_updated_at` と重複する可能性**\n   - `_updated_at` はメタカラムとしてレコード更新を追跡し、`last_updated_at` はコンテンツ更新日時（公開後の更新など）を示すなら意図が明確。しかし命名や意図をコメントで補足した方が良い。\n\n---\n\n**修正必須**\n\n```sql\n-- categories の _updated_at トリガーを追加\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_categories_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON categories\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at();\n```\n\n`last_updated_at` の用途については要件を確認してください。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":641,"cache_read_input_tokens":7204,"output_tokens":400,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":641,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZHqzyazFM6eVxQ4mNX66","type":"assistant","uuid":"9276d304-5402-43fc-90a1-3fe5619a2cef","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:00:52.615Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"d6c1023f-0aa7-4494-96ba-45f65a369f36","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"enumerated-spinning-grove"}
