{"parentUuid":"4415a9f4-8084-47a1-8bbf-66eb2d0d1744","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01K8xdR38EmNbs6mH8C88qkR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":502,"cache_read_input_tokens":7845,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":502},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZHr5BjLu5MwT3JKkkNww","type":"assistant","uuid":"82bae4b0-b6d9-42ea-8234-85acbb020792","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:01:57.266Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"d6c1023f-0aa7-4494-96ba-45f65a369f36","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"enumerated-spinning-grove"}
{"parentUuid":"82bae4b0-b6d9-42ea-8234-85acbb020792","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01K8xdR38EmNbs6mH8C88qkR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PostgreSQL の **Event Trigger** を使えば可能です。\n\n`ddl_command_end` イベントで `CREATE TABLE` 時に発火し、自動でトリガーを設定できます。\n\n```sql\nCREATE FUNCTION auto_set_updated_at_trigger()\nRETURNS event_trigger AS $$\nDECLARE\n    obj record;\n    table_name text;\nBEGIN\n    FOR obj IN\n        SELECT * FROM pg_event_trigger_ddl_commands()\n        WHERE command_tag = 'CREATE TABLE' AND object_type = 'table'\n    LOOP\n        table_name := split_part(obj.object_identity, '.', 2);\n        EXECUTE format(\n            'CREATE TRIGGER trigger_%s_updated_at\n             BEFORE UPDATE ON %s\n             FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at()',\n            table_name,\n            obj.object_identity\n        );\n    END LOOP;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\nCREATE EVENT TRIGGER auto_updated_at_trigger\n    ON ddl_command_end\n    WHEN TAG IN ('CREATE TABLE')\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION auto_set_updated_at_trigger();\n```\n\n**注意点**\n\n- Event Trigger の作成には **superuser 権限**が必要\n- `_updated_at` カラムを持たないテーブル（例: 中間テーブルなど）にもトリガーが設定されてしまう\n  - 除外したいテーブルは命名規則で判定するか、手動で `DROP TRIGGER` が必要\n\nプロジェクトルール上「全テーブルに `_updated_at` を用意する」とあるので、基本的には有効な選択肢です。導入しますか？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":502,"cache_read_input_tokens":7845,"output_tokens":1530,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":502,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZHr5BjLu5MwT3JKkkNww","type":"assistant","uuid":"e358ebff-a6bd-4cf2-9f1c-59ef66a433a7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:02:02.232Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","se